She is amazing!!
Now, from a desperate fan, how could I get in touch with Taylor Swift herself? I'm Brazilian and this time I won't be able to go to the show, but I'd like to ask her to play a song that I'm writing for someone when she came to Sao Paulo this year. There's a boy I love and will probably be on the show and I'm trying to win him back because he's everything to me. If you can help me, I can pay some value if you make a budget. I need help because I'd do anything for love because of this guy and I need him to know that, even if it doesn't work. Please think about it. Thank you, Taylor! S2
